thaai ( tamil : &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1994 indian tamil film , directed by m. a. thirumugam and produced by sandow m. m. a. chinnappa thevar . the film stars m. g. ramachandran , k. r. vijaya and b. saroja devi in lead roles . the film had musical score by v. kumar and b. saroja devi in lead roles . the film had musical score by v. kumar .